data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET. BUYERS FINANCE FELL THROUGHWelcome home to 1418 Aton in the heart of Oak Cliff. This wonderfully remodeled pier and beam house is move in ready. It has 3 ample bedrooms that are not too common in newer homes. The upgraded widows are a huge plus. A one car garage will store your everyday car while the backyard has plenty of room to store a boat or work vehicle. Enjoy the large backyard with plenty of space for gatherings.
